OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud and
OL,6,Fpatchy rain across parts of Scotland,
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland and northern England.
OL,8,FLargely dry elsewhere, with clear
OL,9,Fspells and perhaps the odd light
OL,10,Fshowers. A mild night for most.
